    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is preserved in showroom condition, reflecting a standard of care rarely seen on the secondary market. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, confirms its status as a premier acquisition for the discerning collector. Mechanically beyond reproach and aesthetically perfect, this unit represents an uncompromising investment in performance and luxury.",
