    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this absolute gem. It is in truly stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like a total dream. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been perfectly babied and is ready for its next adventure, this is the one. It's spotless inside and out, and I'm sure you're going to love it. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
