      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen utilizes the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis is structurally sound with no subframe stress fractures, and the suspension maintains its original kinematic integrity. Recent compression and leak-down tests confirm the engine is operating at peak volumetric efficiency. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, free of oxidation or mechanical patina, representing a true collector-tier example of Bavarian engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
