      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously garage-kept and professionally detailed, featuring a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely zero scratches, chips, or swirl marks. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains supple and completely unmarked, with no signs of wear on the bolsters or controls. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced navigation suite, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach; it comes with a complete, documented service history from authorized dealerships, ensuring it has received only the highest level of preventative maintenance. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage is free of debris or corrosion. This is a rare find for a discerning collector or buyer seeking a vehicle in pristine condition. Includes both original keys, all factory manuals, and a transferable ceramic coating warranty.",
